  "status": "Stagnant",
  "summary": "The following standard allows for the implementation of a standard API for [ERC-20](./eip-20.md) token upgrades. This standard specifies an interface that supports the conversion of tokens from one contract (called the \"source token\") to those from another (called the \"destination token\"), as well as several helper methods to provide basic information about the token upgrade (i.e. the address of the source and destination token contracts, the ratio that source will be upgraded to destination, etc.).",
  "title": "Generic Token Upgrade Standard"
